PrecisAppointment of JEAN BRUNET, of Lac Beauport, Quebec, JOHN F. HELLIWELL, O.C., of Vancouver, British Columbia, GORDON RITCHIE, of Ottawa, Ontario, SHAWNA K. VOGEL, of Edmonton, Alberta, and GILBERT R. WINHAM, of Bedford, Nova Scotia, to be on the roster of panellists required by Article 1705 of the Agreement on Internal Trade, to hold office during pleasure for a term of five years.
